    "body": "Please read the [notes](%28http://ipython.org/ipython-doc/2/whatsnew/version2.0.html#modal-user-interface%29) about the keyboard shortcut interface that have changed in 2.0 almost 1 and a half year ago . \n\nCtrl+m is not used any more, and you are, as expected in command mode after entering one of theses shortcut, you do not need to use the mouse but just get back into edit mode. \n"
